"IoT Sentinel: Anomaly Detection System" represents a crucial advancement in IoT security, leveraging machine learning to provide proactive and effective protection against potential threats. By continuously monitoring and analyzing IoT device behavior, it aims to enhance the reliability, security, and resilience of interconnected devices in various domains.
